            <history-note id="DLM1236475"><amended-provision>Section 6(2)(b)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 April 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1107214">section 29(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Taxation (KiwiSaver) Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 110).</history-note>
